Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,欢迎加入OCR小组 qq群906722936 字幕优先发布于群内 字幕广告招租 商业合作Q:1585235535
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:20.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,《比利小子》前情提要\N{\rYUANWEN}Previously, on Billy the Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:22.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先生们 我是来确保\N{\rYUANWEN}Gentlemen, I'm here to ensure the safety
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:24.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,妇女和儿童安全的\N{\rYUANWEN}of the women and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:27.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我警告你们所有人 马上回家\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm warning all of you to go home, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.49,0:00:29.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们为什么不离开呢 离开林肯\N{\rYUANWEN}Why don't we try and leave; get out of Lincoln?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:31.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,查理 我们不能再逃亡了\N{\rYUANWEN}Charlie, we're not runnin' again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:33.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果达德利信守诺言 保持中立\N{\rYUANWEN}If Dudley sticks to his word and stays neutral,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:35.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们在投降后也许会被护送出去\N{\rYUANWEN}we may get escorted out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:38.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们不会出来的 所以我们得把他们引出来\N{\rYUANWEN}They're not comin' out. So we need to get them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:40.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,莱利在酝酿什么诡计\N{\rYUANWEN}Riley's up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:42.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们把他们熏出来\N{\rYUANWEN}We burn them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:46.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,给房子放把火 他们会连哭带叫跑出来的\N{\rYUANWEN}Set fire to the house and they'll come squealin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:47.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把它烧毁\N{\rYUANWEN}Burn it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:55.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果比利和查理有麻烦了 我们应该尽力帮助他们。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:00:59.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你应该保持中立\N{\rYUANWEN}You're supposed to be neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:01.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不该偏袒任何一方 让我们过去\N{\rYUANWEN}You're not supposed to take sides. Let us pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:02.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rYUANWEN}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:08.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们必须做点什么\N{\rYUANWEN}We have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:10.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们还能做什么呢\N{\rYUANWEN}What else could we possibly do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:11.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要去找达德利上校 我要让他\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm going to Colonel Dudley. I'm going to ask him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:12.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,阻止这种疯狂\N{\rYUANWEN}to stop this madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:14.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:16.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他和莱利是一个鼻孔出气\N{\rYUANWEN}He's hand in glove with Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,0:01:19.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我说过了 我不会因为你请求就出手干涉\N{\rYUANWEN}I've already told you. I will not interfere on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:22.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,卡特伦先生非常担心 莱利先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Catron is actually very concerned, Mr. Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:24.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,林肯现在顶着谋杀之都的名头\N{\rYUANWEN}Now with the reputation as a murder capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:26.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,作为一个不法之徒出没的地方\N{\rYUANWEN}as a lawless outlaw infested place,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:28.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谁还肯把钱投资到林肯县\N{\rYUANWEN}who is going to invest their money in Lincoln County?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.01,0:01:30.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利永远不会投降的\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy ain't ever gonna surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:33.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这太疯狂了 根本说不通啊 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, that's crazy! That makes no sense, Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:36.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你怎么就不明白呢 莱利\N{\rYUANWEN}Why don't you ever get it, Riley?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:39.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这家伙是比利小子\N{\rYUANWEN}You're talking about Billy the Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:41.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他妈的比利小字\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy the fuckin' Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:45.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他跟你\N{\rYUANWEN}He is different...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:47.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不一样\N{\rYUANWEN}...from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:48.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他跟我也不一样\N{\rYUANWEN}and he is different from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:54.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,治安官 我没想到会看到\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff, I had not thought to see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,0:01:56.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这么多生命陨落\N{\rYUANWEN}so many lives undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:57.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这就是我们林肯的做法\N{\rYUANWEN}That has been the way of it here in Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:01.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但事实是 你让比利小子跑掉了\N{\rYUANWEN}But the fact remains that you let Billy the Kid escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:04.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,治安官 我强烈建议你\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff, I strongly advise you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:06.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一定要抓到他\N{\rYUANWEN}to hunt him down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:08.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,将他从美国人的想象中\N{\rYUANWEN}and remove him, forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:11.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,永远抹去\N{\rYUANWEN}from the American imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:18.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:22.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,莱利先生 找我有事吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Riley. What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.98,0:02:24.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你听到消息了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Have you heard the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:25.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么消息\N{\rYUANWEN}What news is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:27.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,阿克斯特尔总督\N{\rYUANWEN}The news of Governor Axtell
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:29.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,被免职的消息\N{\rYUANWEN}having been removed from office.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:31.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,显然 这是沃伦·安吉尔先生的\N{\rYUANWEN}Apparently, it's the result of an investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:33.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,调查结果导致的\N{\rYUANWEN}by one Mr. Warren Angel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且新总督也已就位\N{\rYUANWEN}and that we've already a new governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:37.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他叫卢·华莱士\N{\rYUANWEN}His name is Lew Wallace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:39.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他提出对所有\N{\rYUANWEN}He's offering a general amnesty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:41.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,战争中的罪人进行大赦\N{\rYUANWEN}to just about everyone guilty of crimes during the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:45.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只要他们愿意上交枪支 并承诺\N{\rYUANWEN}so long as they are willing to hand over their guns
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:47.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,放弃一切暴力行为\N{\rYUANWEN}and renounce all forms of violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:49.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哦 当然\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们知道这会有用 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}We know that's gonna work. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:53.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但大赦不适用于那些\N{\rYUANWEN}The amnesty doesn't apply to those
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,已经被指控谋杀的人\N{\rYUANWEN}already indicted for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:57.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我自己也分到了任务 要组建一个民兵队\N{\rYUANWEN}I myself have been tasked with forming a posse
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:02.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去抓捕冲突两方中\N{\rYUANWEN}to hunt down the worst and most violent gunslingers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:03.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,最凶狠的枪手\N{\rYUANWEN}on both sides of the conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:05.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,该去抓谁\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:07.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你心里知道 治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}who you've got to find, Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是比利小子\N{\rYUANWEN}It's the Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:11.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,近一半的枪击案都是他所为\N{\rYUANWEN}He's behind almost half the shootings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:13.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只要阻止他 就能阻止杀戮\N{\rYUANWEN}You stop him, you stop the killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:16.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我手上有一张比利小子的逮捕令\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, I am holding warrants for the arrest of Billy the Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:17.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rYUANWEN}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:19.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还有对杰西·埃文斯\N{\rYUANWEN}But also Jesse Evans
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:21.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和其他七河帮成员的逮捕令\N{\rYUANWEN}and members of the Seven Rivers Gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:25.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不会站队的\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm not here to take sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:38.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们知道你跟比利小子是朋友\N{\rYUANWEN}We know that you and the Kid were uh, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:40.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许这就是你对他如此温柔的原因\N{\rYUANWEN}That might explain why you're soft on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:43.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:48.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,祝日安\N{\rYUANWEN}Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:04.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们可能想看看这个\N{\rYUANWEN}Y'all might want to look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:09.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,新任的总督卢·华莱士\N{\rYUANWEN}Recently installed State Governor, Lew Wallace,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:13.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,准备视察林肯县 并要大赦所有\N{\rYUANWEN}set to travel to Lincoln County to offer a general amnesty
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:16.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,参与林肯战争的人员\N{\rYUANWEN}to all involved in the recent Lincoln County War,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:19.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只要他们上缴枪支 放弃暴力\N{\rYUANWEN}if they give up their guns and renounce violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:20.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只要他们上缴枪支 放弃暴力\N{\rYUANWEN}if they give up their guns and renounce violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:23.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这场战争中最臭名昭著的人物\N{\rYUANWEN}The most infamous character involved in the war
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:24.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就是那个法外之徒 比利小子\N{\rYUANWEN}is the outlaw Billy the Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:28.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们如果真的赦免我们\N{\rYUANWEN}If they're offering us a pardon,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:29.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那这笔交易还挺划算\N{\rYUANWEN}I think that's a pretty good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听着 我们对这个新任的\N{\rYUANWEN}Look, we don't know anything about this new...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,华莱士总督并不熟悉 好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Governor Wallace, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他或许是我们翻身的希望\N{\rYUANWEN}He may be our best chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:40.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我们必须小心谨慎\N{\rYUANWEN}but we have to tread carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们要做什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:52.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,加勒特会来找我们的\N{\rYUANWEN}Garrett's gonna come looking for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们需要保持低调 试试这个新总督的成色\N{\rYUANWEN}We need to lay low, see what this new governor does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你要是想去墨西哥 和家人团聚\N{\rYUANWEN}If you need to go to Mexico to be with your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我可以理解\N{\rYUANWEN}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:06.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 我选择和你在一起 甚至一起战斗\N{\rYUANWEN}No, I choose to stay with you and fight if I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:08.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:13.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,拿上这个 照顾好自己 好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Take this. Look after yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:19.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们去去就回\N{\rYUANWEN}We'll be home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:32.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我爱你   -我也是\N{\rYUANWEN}- I love you. - Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:36.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利 我们今后都会这样了\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy, it's always gonna be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:39.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们永远都会被追杀\N{\rYUANWEN}We're always gonna be hunted and hounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:42.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们绝不可能获得自由 在这里不行\N{\rYUANWEN}We're never gonna get free. Not around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:43.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,除非情况有所改变\N{\rYUANWEN}Not until somethin' changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:46.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道 乔治\N{\rYUANWEN}I know, George.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:55.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,伙计们 骑到拉斯塔布拉斯需要一天呢\N{\rYUANWEN}AII right, boys, it's a day's ride to Las Tablas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:59.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,胡安·帕特隆的朋友还在等我们 走吧 上马\N{\rYUANWEN}Juan Patron's friend is waitin' us, let's go. Git up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来吧 我们走\N{\rYUANWEN}Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:34.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,拉斯塔布拉斯 新墨西哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rYUANWEN}Hola.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:43.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你好 先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Hola, Sefior.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\rYUANWEN}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:47.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利 欢迎你和你的朋友来到我的镇子 拉斯塔布拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:48.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Gracias.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:52.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,胡安·帕特伦告诉我你们在路上了 我们听说了你的事迹
