Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rYUANWEN}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:15.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-马上去林肯  -是 卡特伦先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Get into Lincoln right away. - Yes, Mr. Catron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:23.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对了 华尔兹 我女儿怎么样了\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, Walz, how's my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:29.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她很好\N{\rYUANWEN}She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:34.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢关心 卡特伦先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you, Mr. Catron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:37.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她怎么还没怀孕 我想抱孙子\N{\rYUANWEN}Why isn't she pregnant? I want grandkids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:38.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是她的问题还是你的问题\N{\rYUANWEN}Is it her fault or yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:41.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们在试了\N{\rYUANWEN}We're trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:45.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许你打的是空包弹\N{\rYUANWEN}Maybe you're firing blanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:46.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你懂我的意思吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嘿 谢谢你\N{\rYUANWEN}Hey. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:23.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有你的一封信\N{\rYUANWEN}There's a letter for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:26.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谁寄来的\N{\rYUANWEN}A letter from who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:29.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:47.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,上面写什么了\N{\rYUANWEN}What's it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:56.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,上面说莱利和浩世想讲和\N{\rYUANWEN}It says Riley and the House want to make peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:00.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要我们去镇中心见面\N{\rYUANWEN}They want us to meet in the center of town,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:03.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不会有官员在场 只会有一个叫埃德加·沃尔兹的人\N{\rYUANWEN}no officials present, just this man named Edgar Walz
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:05.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他为托马斯·卡特伦工作\N{\rYUANWEN}who works for Thomas Catron.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:09.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他会列出讲和的条款\N{\rYUANWEN}He's gonna lay out the terms of the treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:11.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你怎么看\N{\rYUANWEN}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:14.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,前提是他们能保证我们在林肯的安全\N{\rYUANWEN}I mean, they'd have to guarantee our safety in Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:16.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希望渺茫\N{\rYUANWEN}That's a long shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:17.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,绝对的\N{\rYUANWEN}It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:22.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,除非他们在担心华莱士总督\N{\rYUANWEN}Unless they're afraid of Governor Wallace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:32.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他愿意过来讲和\N{\rYUANWEN}He's willing to come in...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:35.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只要我们能保证他的安全\N{\rYUANWEN}as long as we can guarantee his safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:39.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rYUANWEN}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.97,0:21:42.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们搞得他东躲西藏\N{\rYUANWEN}We've got the boy on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:44.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他很绝望 所以才愿意谈谈\N{\rYUANWEN}He's desperate, that's why he's willing to talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:46.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和平和宽恕的事\N{\rYUANWEN}peace and pardons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:49.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不如咱们让晾他一段时间\N{\rYUANWEN}I say we let him twist in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,朽木不可雕也\N{\rYUANWEN}You really are not that smart, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:55.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们当然要跟目前\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course we should meet the man
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:58.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,最危险的敌人见上一面 越快越好\N{\rYUANWEN}who's the biggest danger to us all, as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:22:01.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西 马上给他回信\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, Jesse, write back to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:03.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,告诉他和谈讲如期举行\N{\rYUANWEN}Tell him that the meeting will go through
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:07.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们会保障他的安全\N{\rYUANWEN}and that his safety is in fact guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:09.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且必须尽快\N{\rYUANWEN}And that it has to be soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:11.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,以防新总督从中作梗\N{\rYUANWEN}or this new Governor's going to wreck our plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:18.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你 莱利\N{\rYUANWEN}I've told you before, Riley,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.59,0:22:19.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这场战争必须结束\N{\rYUANWEN}this war has got to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.68,0:22:24.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,林肯的所有生意都被毁了 包括你的\N{\rYUANWEN}It's ruining every business in Lincoln, including yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:29.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:02.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先生们 晚上好\N{\rYUANWEN}Gentlemen, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.55,0:23:04.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我叫埃德加·华尔兹 我是\N{\rYUANWEN}My name is Edgar Walz and I represent
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:06.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,托马斯·卡特伦先生的商业代表\N{\rYUANWEN}the business interests of Mr. Thomas Catron,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.64,0:23:10.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你一定听说过他了\N{\rYUANWEN}of whom by now you must have surely heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.72,0:23:15.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们是为和平而来 所以 烦请各位\N{\rYUANWEN}We are here to make peace. So, may I ask you to kindly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.40,0:23:18.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把枪和其他武器\N{\rYUANWEN}leave your, um, guns and other weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.48,0:23:20.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,放在那边\N{\rYUANWEN}just over there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.19,0:23:22.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,然后我们再走上街头 开始会谈\N{\rYUANWEN}before we go out to our meeting in the street?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:24.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那另一方呢\N{\rYUANWEN}What about the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.03,0:23:28.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我对他们也是同样的要求\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, I have made the same request to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:29.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,除非所有人都上缴枪械\N{\rYUANWEN}And I will not convene this meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.70,0:23:31.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,否则会议不会开始\N{\rYUANWEN}until all guns have been surrendered.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:35.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我向你保证\N{\rYUANWEN}You have my assurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.11,0:24:08.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们 先生们\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.07,0:24:12.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好了 那么请大家跟我来吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, if you would be so kind to follow me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.81,0:24:38.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先生们 请靠近一点\N{\rYUANWEN}Gentlemen, please come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.06,0:24:42.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听着 我们来此的原因不用多说\N{\rYUANWEN}Listen, you all know why you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.28,0:24:45.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们都是来讲和的\N{\rYUANWEN}We've come to make peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.94,0:24:48.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,以下是讲和的条款\N{\rYUANWEN}These are the terms of the peace treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.11,0:24:52.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大家准备好了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is everybody ready to listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.24,0:24:54.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,准备好了\N{\rYUANWEN}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.08,0:24:58.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,本合约规定如下\N{\rYUANWEN}This treaty states
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.42,0:25:01.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,任意一方都不能杀害\N{\rYUANWEN}that no one on either side can kill anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.13,0:25:04.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,另一方的人马 否则条约失效\N{\rYUANWEN}on the other side without withdrawing from this treaty;
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.63,0:25:06.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,双方都不会在民事诉讼中\N{\rYUANWEN}and that neither party will give evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.92,0:25:09.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,提供对对方不利的证据\N{\rYUANWEN}in a civil prosecution against the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.30,0:25:14.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,双方还将提供一切可能的援助\N{\rYUANWEN}Also that both sides will render all possible aid
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.35,0:25:17.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,避免任何一方的人逮捕\N{\rYUANWEN}in resisting the arrest of anyone on either side.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.85,0:25:20.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,以及\N{\rYUANWEN}And.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.85,0:25:24.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,任何违反该合约的人\N{\rYUANWEN}anyone who fails to live up to this agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.49,0:25:27.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,将被处死\N{\rYUANWEN}...will be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.16,0:25:37.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大家都同意这些条款吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Does everyone agree with the terms?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.04,0:25:39.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别无异议\N{\rYUANWEN}No other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.83,0:25:43.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rYUANWEN}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.38,0:25:45.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在 真诚地握个手\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, shake hands like you mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.84,0:25:50.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都过去了 我们就是来讲和的\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, fuck it, it's what we're here to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.01,0:25:57.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,瞧 也没那么难吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Wasn't so hard, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.52,0:26:02.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是好事 我们讲和了\N{\rYUANWEN}This is good. We made peacel
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.69,0:26:05.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我提议大家庆祝一场\N{\rYUANWEN}- - I say we celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.34,0:26:26.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rYUANWEN}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.01,0:26:34.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这很开心吧\N{\rYUANWEN}This is a good bit of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.85,0:26:38.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是啊 希望不是昙花一现\N{\rYUANWEN}Sure. I just hope it lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.27,0:26:41.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,啊 你太过担心了\N{\rYUANWEN}Ah, you worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.06,0:26:45.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你一向如此  -而你一向不够\N{\rYUANWEN}- You always did. And you never worry enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.52,0:26:49.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还记得很久之前\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you remember that girl
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.23,0:26:51.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我俩都喜欢的那个女孩吗\N{\rYUANWEN}we were both interested in a while back?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.11,0:26:54.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然 芭芭拉\N{\rYUANWEN}Sure. Barbara.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.20,0:26:55.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Mmm. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.70,0:26:58.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很好奇她现在在哪里\N{\rYUANWEN}I wonder where she's at right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.45,0:27:02.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.41,0:27:05.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可能在给孩子做晚饭\N{\rYUANWEN}Probably making her kids supper,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.63,0:27:07.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哄她们上康睡觉吧\N{\rYUANWEN}tuckinem into bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.38,0:27:12.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,感觉像是一百年前的事了\N{\rYUANWEN}You know, it feels like 100 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.88,0:27:15.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,赶着牛儿去放牧\N{\rYUANWEN}running cattle off the range.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.14,0:27:19.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那时光多美好啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Those were some good times.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.97,0:27:22.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,确实很美好\N{\rYUANWEN}They were somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.98,0:27:27.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可惜没有什么是永垂不朽\N{\rYUANWEN}I guess nothing lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.90,0:27:30.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不许你给我煽情 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't get sentimental on me now, Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.66,0:27:41.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,回头见 小子\N{\rYUANWEN}See ya around, Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.25,0:27:50.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-嘿  -慢着 等等\N{\rYUANWEN}- Hey. - Whoa, whoa, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.09,0:27:51.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-嘿 嘿 嘿   -看着点啊\N{\rYUANWEN}- Hey, hey, hey, hey. Watch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.10,0:28:03.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别怪我哈 小子\N{\rYUANWEN}No hard feelings, Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.14,0:28:08.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,啊 小怪一下而已 莱利先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Ah. Just a few, Mr. Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.98,0:28:11.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,小怪一下\N{\rYUANWEN}Just a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.78,0:28:21.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,喂 给我来杯酒 嘿\N{\rYUANWEN}Give me a drink. Hey. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.87,0:28:25.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,帮我照顾好这个年轻人\N{\rYUANWEN}You take care of that young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.46,0:28:27.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-晚安 小子们  -晚安\N{\rYUANWEN}Good night, boys. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.21,0:28:31.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,晚安 各位\N{\rYUANWEN}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.50,0:28:33.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,各位\N{\rYUANWEN}Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.97,0:28:36.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想现在请你们所有人\N{\rYUANWEN}I want to treat y'all
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.55,0:28:40.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去卡莱姆吃牡蛎大餐\N{\rYUANWEN}to an oyster supper at Callum's right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.97,0:28:42.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都谁要来\N{\rYUANWEN}Who's comin' with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.68,0:28:46.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,走吧 大家一起\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's go, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.03,0:28:56.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,莱利去哪儿了\N{\rYUANWEN}Where's Riley?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.58,0:29:11.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 看看那是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, well, look who's comin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.67,0:29:19.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-嘿  -那是麦克斯温太太的律师\N{\rYUANWEN}- Hey. That's Mrs. McSween's lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.26,0:29:22.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字\N{\rYUANWEN}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.76,0:29:25.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先生 我叫查普曼\N{\rYUANWEN}My name, sir, is Chapman.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.97,0:29:27.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哦对\N{\rYUANWEN}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.56,0:29:28.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你就是那个了不起的律师\N{\rYUANWEN}You're that fancy lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.02,0:29:30.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,想把我们告上法庭的律师\N{\rYUANWEN}that's tryin' to take us to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.02,0:29:34.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你给我们跳支舞如何\N{\rYUANWEN}I think you should dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.86,0:29:42.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么鬼 奥林杰 我们讲和了\N{\rYUANWEN}What the hell, Olinger? We made peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.78,0:29:45.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利小子说得对\N{\rYUANWEN}Kid's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.79,0:29:51.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们讲和了 各位\N{\rYUANWEN}We made peace, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.47,0:29:59.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道我是谁吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.22,0:30:02.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先生 你是莱利先生\N{\rYUANWEN}You, sir, are Mr. Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.89,0:30:04.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,再说一遍我的名字\N{\rYUANWEN}Say my name again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.56,0:30:07.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,莱利\N{\rYUANWEN}Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.06,0:30:10.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没错 你个混蛋\N{\rYUANWEN}That's right, you fuckin' arsehole.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.48,0:30:14.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请让我过去 先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Let me pass, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.57,0:30:16.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,莱利 让他过去\N{\rYUANWEN}Riley, let him pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.57,0:30:19.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哦我草\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.28,0:30:24.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利小子想让我放他过去\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy the Kid wants me to let him pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.41,0:30:26.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先生 让我走吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Sir, let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.79,0:30:29.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rYUANWEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.72,0:30:41.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们得走了 汤姆\N{\rYUANWEN}We gotta go, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.93,0:30:47.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,小子们 我们去吃牡蛎吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, boys, let's go get those oysters.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.12,0:31:14.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-华莱士总督  -我猜你是沃特利吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Governor Wallace. - Mr. Wortley, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.37,0:31:15.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,随时为您效劳先生\N{\rYUANWEN}At your service, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.88,0:31:17.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是你的旅馆吗\N{\rYUANWEN}This is your establishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.46,0:31:20.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,太棒了 请帮我拿下行李\N{\rYUANWEN}Wonderful. Take my bags, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.30,0:31:21.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然可以 先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.38,0:31:25.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,乐意至极\N{\rYUANWEN}Pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.51,0:31:27.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,上校\N{\rYUANWEN}Colonel,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.51,0:31:29.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请骑马到斯坦顿堡\N{\rYUANWEN}ride up to Fort Stanton,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.02,0:31:31.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,告诉达德利上校我想见他\N{\rYUANWEN}tell Colonel Dudley I'd like to see him
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.81,0:31:32.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,速去 谢谢你\N{\rYUANWEN}immediately, please. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.83,0:31:57.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,总督\N{\rYUANWEN}Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.25,0:31:58.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,上校 稍息\N{\rYUANWEN}Colonel, at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.67,0:31:59.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.01,0:32:04.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,上校\N{\rYUANWEN}Colonel,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.01,0:32:06.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这就是你对林肯事件的\N{\rYUANWEN}is this your official report
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.55,0:32:08.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,正式报告吗\N{\rYUANWEN}for the events that happened in Lincoln?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.85,0:32:10.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 长官\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.89,0:32:14.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,相信您已从我报告中得知\N{\rYUANWEN}As you have no doubt ascertained from reading my report,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.23,0:32:17.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当时的情况让我不能无动于衷\N{\rYUANWEN}the situation I faced at that time was untenable.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.60,0:32:19.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在没有其他合法权力的情况下\N{\rYUANWEN}And it was with great reluctance
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.02,0:32:22.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只能勉为其难\N{\rYUANWEN}and lack of any other lawful authority
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.40,0:32:24.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,命令我的部队进入林肯\N{\rYUANWEN}that I ordered my troops into Lincoln
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.53,0:32:28.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,恢复秩序 保护妇女和儿童的安全\N{\rYUANWEN}to restore order and to protect the women and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.12,0:32:29.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 上校\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.37,0:32:31.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的上一任 阿克塞尔总督\N{\rYUANWEN}Did my predecessor, Governor Axtell,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.04,0:32:33.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,授权你行动了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}authorize your actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.58,0:32:35.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他暗示我这么做是对的\N{\rYUANWEN}He implied that I was doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.04,0:32:40.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,达德利上校\N{\rYUANWEN}Colonel Dudley,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.55,0:32:43.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,遵照麦克唐纳将军的命令\N{\rYUANWEN}you are hereby removed from your command,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.88,0:32:45.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,特此解除你的职务\N{\rYUANWEN}by the order of General Macdonald,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.80,0:32:47.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,立即生效\N{\rYUANWEN}effective immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.63,0:32:50.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在审查过证据后 我同意他的判断\N{\rYUANWEN}I have reviewed the evidence, and I concur with his judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.56,0:32:54.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你以美国陆军的名义 违反了命令\N{\rYUANWEN}Against all protocols in the name of the U. S. Army
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.73,0:32:56.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在这场争端中站队了\N{\rYUANWEN}you took sides in this dispute.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.06,0:32:58.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你允许烧毁那栋房子\N{\rYUANWEN}You allowed the burning of that house,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.73,0:33:01.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你允许谋杀麦克斯温\N{\rYUANWEN}and you allowed the murder of McSween.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.11,0:33:02.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这种行为十分可耻\N{\rYUANWEN}It's disgraceful conduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.57,0:33:07.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,再见了 上校\N{\rYUANWEN}Good day, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.66,0:33:17.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,再见 长官\N{\rYUANWEN}Good day to you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.76,0:33:32.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,过来吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.93,0:33:34.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰 总督\N{\rYUANWEN}Begging your pardon, Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.27,0:33:38.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我冒昧地给您倒了一杯\N{\rYUANWEN}But I've taken the liberty of bringing you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.10,0:33:40.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我最好的威士忌\N{\rYUANWEN}my finest whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.27,0:33:42.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢 沃特利先生 你真贴心\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you, Mr. Wortley. That's very kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.81,0:33:44.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这封信是什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What's that letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.53,0:33:46.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有人给你送来的 先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Someone just dropped it off for you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.65,0:33:50.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢 沃特利先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you, Mr. Wortley.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.66,0:33:58.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,华莱士总督\N{\rYUANWEN}Governor Wallace,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.33,0:34:00.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我回到林肯是为了讲和\N{\rYUANWEN}I came to Lincoln to make peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.96,0:34:02.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,想要拥抱和平\N{\rYUANWEN}to lay aside my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.79,0:34:08.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但浩世集团又一次破坏了这种和平\N{\rYUANWEN}But once again, the House has destroyed that peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.34,0:34:10.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我希望你能信守承诺\N{\rYUANWEN}I hope that you are true to your word
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.97,0:34:13.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也希望你是真的想帮林肯洗清污名\N{\rYUANWEN}and that you really do want to help clean up Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.05,0:34:16.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,昨晚 我目睹了一位律师被谋杀\N{\rYUANWEN}Last night, I witnessed the murder of the lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.47,0:34:19.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他叫休斯顿·查普曼 我可以指证凶手的名字\N{\rYUANWEN}Huston Chapman, and I can testify to the killer's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.98,0:34:22.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我因为林肯之战中的事\N{\rYUANWEN}I have indictments against me for what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.15,0:34:23.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,受到起诉\N{\rYUANWEN}in the Lincoln County War,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.98,0:34:26.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我害怕如果我束手投降\N{\rYUANWEN}and I fear that if I give myself up,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.40,0:34:27.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的敌人会杀了我\N{\rYUANWEN}my enemies will kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.82,0:34:30.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但如果这些起诉能被撤销\N{\rYUANWEN}But if these indictments can be annulled,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.99,0:34:32.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会告诉您一切\N{\rYUANWEN}I will tell all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.70,0:34:34.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我叫基德·安特里姆\N{\rYUANWEN}My name is Kid Antrim.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.41,0:34:37.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利小子\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy the Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.75,0:34:49.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,安特里姆先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Antrim.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.34,0:34:52.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请在小心进入林肯县后\N{\rYUANWEN}Proceed carefully into Lincoln
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.18,0:34:55.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去旧粮仓大楼见我\N{\rYUANWEN}and make your way to the old granary building.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.51,0:34:59.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我有权免除对你的起诉\N{\rYUANWEN}I have the authority to exempt you from prosecution
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.10,0:35:01.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意为所知的一切作证\N{\rYUANWEN}if you will testify to what you say that you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.76,0:35:34.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你好啊 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Hello, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.64,0:35:38.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,华莱士总督\N{\rYUANWEN}Governor Wallace.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.89,0:35:42.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,叫我卢就可以\N{\rYUANWEN}Please, you can call me Lew.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.39,0:35:44.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不如坐下聊\N{\rYUANWEN}Why don't you have a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.28,0:36:02.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利 我一直很期待见到你\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy, I have been very anxious to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.50,0:36:06.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我来到这里后 跟很多人都谈过\N{\rYUANWEN}I have spoken to many people since my arrival here in town,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.08,0:36:08.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很多人 墨西哥人 盎格鲁人\N{\rYUANWEN}many people. The Mexicans, the Anglos,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.96,0:36:10.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们都对你评价颇高\N{\rYUANWEN}they all speak very highly of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.75,0:36:13.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也都证实了你的正直和诚实\N{\rYUANWEN}They all testify to your integrity and your honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.80,0:36:18.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利 我想赦免你\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy, I'd like to offer you a pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.93,0:36:21.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,让你重新进入正常世界\N{\rYUANWEN}Allow you to re- enter the ordinary world
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.14,0:36:22.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,做一个守法正派的公民\N{\rYUANWEN}of law- abiding and decent citizens
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.02,0:36:25.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认为你的能力在这里\N{\rYUANWEN}where I think your abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.27,0:36:26.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,肯定会派上大用场\N{\rYUANWEN}well, they will surely flourish.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.77,0:36:32.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听起来很不错 先生\N{\rYUANWEN}That all sounds very nice, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.11,0:36:36.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但这到底怎么实行呢\N{\rYUANWEN}But how exactly is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.16,0:36:41.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,首先\N{\rYUANWEN}First,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.99,0:36:45.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你需要同意 你会留在林肯县\N{\rYUANWEN}you just agree, you commit to sticking around Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.83,0:36:52.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,并指认杀害约翰·h·汤斯顿\N{\rYUANWEN}And you identify the killers of John H. Tunstall
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.30,0:36:54.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和律师休斯顿·查普曼的凶手\N{\rYUANWEN}and the lawyer Huston Chapman.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.97,0:36:58.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,作为交换 我将赦免你那些所谓的罪行\N{\rYUANWEN}In exchange, I will pardon all your alleged offenses
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.80,0:37:00.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,并保证你不会因谋杀\N{\rYUANWEN}and I will ensure that you are not prosecuted
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.80,0:37:02.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,布雷迪治安官的罪名被起诉\N{\rYUANWEN}for the murder of Sheriff Brady.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.14,0:37:08.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.07,0:37:13.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我希望你获得公正\N{\rYUANWEN}I want you to have justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.82,0:37:17.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我希望正义得到伸张\N{\rYUANWEN}And I want justice to be seen to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.74,0:37:19.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,毕竟 我是这里的总督\N{\rYUANWEN}I am the governor, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.00,0:37:26.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一言为定吗 孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}Do we have an agreement, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.43,0:37:43.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一言为定 先生\N{\rYUANWEN}You have a deal, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.42,0:38:12.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,威廉·h·邦尼\N{\rYUANWEN}William H. Bonney.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.75,0:38:14.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你被捕了\N{\rYUANWEN}You're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.55,0:38:17.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把枪放下\N{\rYUANWEN}Put your guns down.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.72,0:38:22.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,帕特\N{\rYUANWEN}Pat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.56,0:38:27.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我早知道你会在这里的\N{\rYUANWEN}I should have known you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.73,0:38:30.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,抱歉了 基德\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm sorry, Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.06,0:38:32.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.78,0:38:42.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,加勒特治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff Garrett,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.24,0:38:44.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,事情比我预期中要好很多\N{\rYUANWEN}that went much better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.08,0:38:47.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你和你的手下表现出色 谢谢你\N{\rYUANWEN}You and your men were excellent. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.24,0:38:48.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 总督\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you, Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.08,0:38:51.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.33,0:38:53.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你和我刚刚逮捕了\N{\rYUANWEN}You and I have just arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.38,0:38:55.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,美国的头号通缉犯\N{\rYUANWEN}the most wanted man in all of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.00,0:38:58.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我猜全国报纸都会报道的\N{\rYUANWEN}I suspect it will be in all the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.09,0:39:00.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我很高兴\N{\rYUANWEN}And I am sure glad
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.34,0:39:03.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想出了引比利上钩的办法\N{\rYUANWEN}that I had the idea of luring Billy into the trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.64,0:39:08.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,等等 这不是我们一起\N{\rYUANWEN}Wait, that's- that's not what we.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.52,0:39:09.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,至少报纸上会这么写啦\N{\rYUANWEN}At least that's what the papers will say,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.98,0:39:11.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是好事啊\N{\rYUANWEN}which is a darn good thing
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.94,0:39:14.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,考虑到今年是选举年\N{\rYUANWEN}given it's an election year and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.65,0:39:16.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在 治安官，\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, Sheriff,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.65,0:39:20.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你的工作是确保比利\N{\rYUANWEN}your job is to make sure that Billy
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.99,0:39:23.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,被安全护送到圣达菲\N{\rYUANWEN}is escorted safely all the way down to Santa Fe,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.86,0:39:27.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,让他及时赶上提审\N{\rYUANWEN}so he can make it in time for his arraignment for trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.20,0:39:28.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别让我失望\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't let me down on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.72,0:39:45.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,下午好 治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}Good afternoon, Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.47,0:39:46.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,下午好\N{\rYUANWEN}Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.64,0:39:54.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我能问你个问题吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.65,0:39:56.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那得看情况\N{\rYUANWEN}That depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.15,0:40:01.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只是很想知道\N{\rYUANWEN}I just can't help wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.99,0:40:03.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这件事最后是什么结果\N{\rYUANWEN}how this whole thing is gonna pan out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.86,0:40:05.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你懂我意思吗\N{\rYUANWEN}If you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.91,0:40:08.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们为你准备了个特别的牢房\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, we've got a special cell for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.83,0:40:15.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好让你远离麻烦\N{\rYUANWEN}so you don't get into any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.67,0:40:17.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在适当的时候 会有人护送你\N{\rYUANWEN}And then, in due course, you will be escorted
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.54,0:40:18.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,离开这里接受审判\N{\rYUANWEN}out of here for trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.42,0:40:26.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,具体罪名是什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What exactly are the charges?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.72,0:40:30.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你和我一样清楚 自己犯了什么罪\N{\rYUANWEN}You know as well as I do what crimes you've committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.93,0:40:32.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哦对\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.94,0:40:37.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你知道吗\N{\rYUANWEN}But, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.52,0:40:40.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我从来没有背叛过朋友\N{\rYUANWEN}I've never betrayed a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.96,0:40:57.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,注意北面\N{\rYUANWEN}Watch the north side.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.42,0:41:01.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有人经过 来吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Comin'through. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.38,0:41:06.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,确保这扇门没人进出\N{\rYUANWEN}Make sure that door does not move.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.93,0:41:08.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,关上大门\N{\rYUANWEN}Close the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.64,0:41:12.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来吧 走吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Come on. Get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.73,0:41:21.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是你的了\N{\rYUANWEN}He is all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.11,0:41:29.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,进去\N{\rYUANWEN}Move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.13,0:41:44.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.63,0:41:49.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有位女士要见你\N{\rYUANWEN}There's a lady here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.19,0:42:02.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,托博斯科小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Senorita del Tobosco.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.44,0:42:05.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么风把您吹来了\N{\rYUANWEN}To what do I owe the pleasure of this visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.44,0:42:07.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我父亲 母亲和哥哥\N{\rYUANWEN}My father, my mother and my brother
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.78,0:42:10.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都被枪杀了 加勒特治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}were all gunned down, Sheriff Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.66,0:42:12.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,到目前为止 您并未为此抓捕任何人\N{\rYUANWEN}So far no one has been arrested for these crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.82,0:42:15.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这一切还在调查中 小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Everything is still under investigation, Senorita.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.54,0:42:17.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我已经向几个人发出了逮捕令\N{\rYUANWEN}And there are arrest warrants out for several people
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.00,0:42:20.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,并要就这些残忍的谋杀问问他们\N{\rYUANWEN}that we want to question about those terrible murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.79,0:42:23.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也和你一样 想看到正义得到伸张\N{\rYUANWEN}Like you, I want to see that justice is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.51,0:42:29.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还有别的事吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.68,0:42:32.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有 我需要你的允许\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes. Apparently, I need your permission
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.80,0:42:35.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,进监狱探望一个犯人\N{\rYUANWEN}to enter the jail and visit a prisoner here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.18,0:42:36.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是说比利小子吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You talkin' about Billy the Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.35,0:42:39.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.86,0:42:45.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我看也无妨\N{\rYUANWEN}I see no harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.70,0:42:51.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不幸的是 我得查一下\N{\rYUANWEN}Unfortunately, I will just have to check
